items.name: CRAB-Contextual-Retrieval-and-Analysis-Bot
items.description: CRAB (Contextual Retrieval and Analysis Bot) is an AI-powered chatbot using Retrieval-Augmented Generation. CRAB integrates ChromaDB for efficient retrieval and LangSmith for monitoring, offering intelligent responses and analysis.
